### Service Desk API — quick tests
### Needs the VS Code extension "REST Client" (id: humao.rest-client).
### Flow: register -> login -> copy the token into @token below -> test tickets.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Register (returns a token + REQUESTER role)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gabrielly",
  "email": "gabi@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "gabi@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. Me (uses the token below)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2NTYxYTc5Yy00Yzk4LTRmNDItYjIxMi03Nzc1MzdiY2RiZjIiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImdhYmlAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3ODQ1ODk1MTEsImV4cCI6MTc4NDY3NTkxMX0.kDGnTBz0gfftRXvOjCU4S1hHy7-KAeqdl7nFapD3onQ

### 5. Create a ticket (any logged-in user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2NTYxYTc5Yy00Yzk4LTRmNDItYjIxMi03Nzc1MzdiY2RiZjIiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImdhYmlAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3ODQ1ODk1MTEsImV4cCI6MTc4NDY3NTkxMX0.kDGnTBz0gfftRXvOjCU4S1hHy7-KAeqdl7nFapD3onQ
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Cannot log into email",
  "description": "Outlook keeps rejecting my password since this morning.",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "category": "access"
}

### 6. List tickets (requester sees own; agent/admin see all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2NTYxYTc5Yy00Yzk4LTRmNDItYjIxMi03Nzc1MzdiY2RiZjIiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImdhYmlAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3ODQ1ODk1MTEsImV4cCI6MTc4NDY3NTkxMX0.kDGnTBz0gfftRXvOjCU4S1hHy7-KAeqdl7nFapD3onQ

### 6b. List only OPEN tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets?status=OPEN
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2NTYxYTc5Yy00Yzk4LTRmNDItYjIxMi03Nzc1MzdiY2RiZjIiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImdhYmlAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3ODQ1ODk1MTEsImV4cCI6MTc4NDY3NTkxMX0.kDGnTBz0gfftRXvOjCU4S1hHy7-KAeqdl7nFapD3onQ

### 7. Get one ticket — paste a ticket id from step 5/6
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/79fbd537-ea25-4571-9845-1c95c017785d
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2NTYxYTc5Yy00Yzk4LTRmNDItYjIxMi03Nzc1MzdiY2RiZjIiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImdhYmlAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3ODQ1ODk1MTEsImV4cCI6MTc4NDY3NTkxMX0.kDGnTBz0gfftRXvOjCU4S1hHy7-KAeqdl7nFapD3onQ

### 8. Add a comment to a ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/79fbd537-ea25-4571-9845-1c95c017785d/comments
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2NTYxYTc5Yy00Yzk4LTRmNDItYjIxMi03Nzc1MzdiY2RiZjIiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImdhYmlAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3ODQ1ODk1MTEsImV4cCI6MTc4NDY3NTkxMX0.kDGnTBz0gfftRXvOjCU4S1hHy7-KAeqdl7nFapD3onQ
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "I already tried resetting it, still no luck."
}

### 9. Update a ticket — AGENT/ADMIN only (403 for a requester)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tickets/79fbd537-ea25-4571-9845-1c95c017785d
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2NTYxYTc5Yy00Yzk4LTRmNDItYjIxMi03Nzc1MzdiY2RiZjIiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImdhYmlAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3ODQ1ODk1MTEsImV4cCI6MTc4NDY3NTkxMX0.kDGnTBz0gfftRXvOjCU4S1hHy7-KAeqdl7nFapD3onQ
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "priority": "URGENT"
}
